<TEXT>
<P>
I am hard-pressed to express my dismay and anger over the brutality so 
graphically depicted in the May 12th episode of "Beauty and the Beast." Our 
family used to love the show for its depth of human compassion and peaceful 
problem solving. What happened? Perhaps kindness and ingenuity don't win 
ratings wars? 
</P>
<P>
Eileen Bigelow, Whittier 
</P>
</TEXT>
