<TEXT>
<P>
In reply to a recent statement in this column, I must stand up for Bill Press 
on Channel 7. I look forward to his appearances and find his comments right on 
target. Nobody pleases everyone but I want Channel 7 to know that Press makes a 
favorable impression on this viewer. 
</P>
<P>
Mildred M. Hurst, Northridge 
</P>
