<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAFE AND SOUND NO MORE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is difficult to describe the intense emotions I felt when I read John 
Doyle's "Safe and Sound No More." It was the first time that someone has dared 
to adequately describe the same painful feelings and emotions that I have 
experienced. Doyle's story is so similar to mine that I could have written it. 
I applaud his courage for sharing this important topic. 
</P>
<P>
NAME WITHHELD 
</P>
<P>
Newport Beach 
</P>
