<P>
I usually agree with Martin Bernheimer -- or as much as anyone can with any 
critic who offers his opinion in "I have spoken" terms -- but not in his 
denigration of Andrew Lloyd Webber's work ("A Smorgasbord of Mush," June 4). 
</P>
