.. . CLOSING QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Feuds have gone on for years, but the stakes are much, much higher now. . . . 
Everybody's in play when something like this happens." 
</P>
<P>
 -- the head of a major Hollywood studio, on Paramount Communications' attempt 
to disrupt the planned merger of Warner Communications and Time Inc. by making 
a cash offer for Time. 
</P>
</TEXT>
