<P>
FOREIGN BUYERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Robert A. Jones' column ("Sayonara to the Best of California," Part I, May 30) 
on the selling and buying, by foreigners, of our best California real estate 
concludes that "This is a game we can no longer afford." Wrong! We could afford 
