warm up for T-ball game. RICK PERRY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Joyce and Jerry 
Nicholson have lived in Cypress for 20 years. HENRY DIROCCO; Table, AT A GLANCE 
; Map, Cypress, California, Los Angeles Times 
