pain-compliance technique to remove him from San Diego clinic. ; Photo, Calm 
prevails at anti-abortion demonstration at La Mesa clinic. ; Photo, 
Anti-abortion protesters jam hallway, blocking access at the La Mesa 
family-planning center. ; Photo, Police officers cordon off some of the 
anti-abortion protesters who barricaded Mission Village clinic. DAVE GATLEY / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
