Boulevard and 47th Street in Los Angeles after the family of Sarah Laureana, 
19, called police. Metoyer, who is being held without bail, was booked on one 
count of murder, three counts of rape and three counts of robbery, said 
Inglewood Sgt. Harold Moret. 
</P>
