<P>
MOVIEGOER LAUDS LISTENING DEVICES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Speaking as a professional with disposable income, I will be honored to dispose 
of part of my income at the Laguna Hills Mann Theatres. Due to my hearing 
impairment, I have limited myself almost exclusively to foreign movies with 
subtitles or legitimate theaters with . . . listening devices. Now a county 
movie theater has added (the) devices. 
</P>
